notes
AEROnomy measurements: D-region probing by radar with (Kero) and without (Turunen) heating (heating 
experiments to be cancelled according to geophysical conditions). Experiments without heating are for 
aerosol measurements. Contact for Antti Kero: antti.kero@sgo.fi
